Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.02,0:01:25.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漫画的版税收到了 大家一起去泡温泉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.28,0:01:29.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？突然把我叫过来 还以为什么事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.01,0:01:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你把那些版税全部用来请我们就没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.19,0:01:35.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我全都用来请啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.43,0:01:41.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样真的好吗 把版税全部用掉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.96,0:01:45.44,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\c&HF3727B&\3c&HFFFFFF&}去泡温泉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.05,0:01:48.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.07,0:01:50.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么把行李都寄放好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.81,0:01:53.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大海啊！泳衣啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.36,0:01:55.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.16,0:01:59.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个丢人的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.95,0:02:01.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得太对了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.95,0:02:07.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师也真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.37,0:02:13.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到大家都穿着泳衣 我真幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.80,0:02:18.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,濑奈 你的泳衣里是不是垫了点东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.86,0:02:21.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为长大了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.12,0:02:22.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.52,0:02:24.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.21,0:02:28.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女人是有自己的自尊心的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.84,0:02:31.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仔细一看 足须小姐和见张也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.53,0:02:36.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太过份了 我只是想看看大家穿泳衣最真实的一面！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.16,0:02:39.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把胸垫什么的都拿掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.15,0:02:40.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.00,0:02:41.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.37,0:02:43.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.39,0:02:44.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家换个心情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.93,0:02:47.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得来到离海边这么近的温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.82,0:02:49.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽情的享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.01,0:02:50.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.18,0:02:52.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么Let's Enioy！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.74,0:02:58.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's 狂拍！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.76,0:03:07.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲奈 你好大胆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.28,0:03:09.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师你个H
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.51,0:03:23.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.81,0:03:33.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这件泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.01,0:03:37.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是足须小姐的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.83,0:03:38.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:41.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胸垫也很厚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.76,0:03:43.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 老师！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.10,0:03:44.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,足须小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.17,0:03:46.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.25,0:03:49.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个被冲走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.88,0:03:53.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能不能帮我拿过来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.89,0:03:58.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的胸部现在是裸露状态？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.75,0:04:00.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你声音太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.82,0:04:02.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上拿过去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.82,0:04:11.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把泳衣给你的时候 不小心看见你的胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.98,0:04:13.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也会当作是事故原谅我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.97,0:04:15.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你不要看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.62,0:04:22.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没好 眼睛先别睁开
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.73,0:04:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.75,0:04:27.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.12,0:04:29.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.08,0:04:33.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实被冲走的不光是上身
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:36.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下身也…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:40.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请别往这边看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.60,0:04:41.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:43.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被冲到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.03,0:04:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.95,0:04:48.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找不到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.46,0:04:50.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那怎么行 这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.49,0:04:53.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,足须小姐No Pants状态会被很多人看到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.24,0:04:54.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,足须小姐的No Pants！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.07,0:04:57.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请别老是说No Pants！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.45,0:04:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.68,0:05:01.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.92,0:05:03.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你穿我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.21,0:05:06.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就算是No Pants也没关系！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.00,0:05:07.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是犯法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.07,0:05:09.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是No Pants…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.80,0:05:11.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这个问题…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.12,0:05:26.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的泳裤也被冲走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.55,0:05:34.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见张她们来了 让她们帮我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.37,0:05:36.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.21,0:05:42.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真倒霉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.85,0:05:46.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为这辈子都要待在海里了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.83,0:05:50.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能发现你们真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.17,0:05:51.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.98,0:05:54.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等！你干嘛跟着过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.71,0:05:55.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.97,0:06:00.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混…浴？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.51,0:06:02.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混浴？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:05.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然 是混浴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.10,0:06:06.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.71,0:06:11.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道这是混浴才故意带我们来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.12,0:06:14.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赤裸相见有时也是很重要的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.45,0:06:15.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.89,0:06:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何都不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:18.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何都不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.80,0:06:20.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.08,0:06:23.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都把所有的版税用掉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.67,0:06:27.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请务必 务必施舍小人一次机会！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.40,0:06:28.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们可怜一下我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.31,0:06:31.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.81,0:06:33.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客…客人们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.97,0:06:37.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么把他的眼睛蒙住怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.87,0:06:43.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好美的风景啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.32,0:06:45.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:47.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是一个好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.78,0:06:49.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相当不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.86,0:06:53.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说今天就我们几个留宿哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.04,0:06:56.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是包场呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:11.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那个 我看不见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.80,0:07:12.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,废话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.91,0:07:16.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好黑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.23,0:07:20.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浴池在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.81,0:07:23.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你一起进来就应该知足了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.69,0:07:25.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.51,0:07:35.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什么啊 爱徒…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.05,0:07:40.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.99,0:07:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我们看到什么东西啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.56,0:07:50.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到我的那个了吗？ H！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.72,0:07:52.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你让我们看到的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.84,0:07:55.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次看到的竟然是你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.11,0:07:59.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.29,0:08:01.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我以死谢罪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.76,0:08:04.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,濑奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.97,0:08:12.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,濑奈？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.73,0:08:17.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.74,0:08:23.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玩得好尽兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.25,0:08:26.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次旅行好愉快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.78,0:08:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须要感谢老师呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.97,0:08:31.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.34,0:08:34.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我总觉得被他耍的团团转
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.08,0:08:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好糟糕的旅行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.73,0:08:40.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 差不多要睡觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.33,0:08:42.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.40,0:08:49.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你跟我们一个房间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.14,0:08:52.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我只订了一个房间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.51,0:08:56.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为…为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.37,0:08:58.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.05,0:09:01.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能和你这种性欲的化身一起睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.75,0:09:04.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.34,0:09:08.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从浴衣的缝隙里露出来的玉足 还有乳沟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.99,0:09:09.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没那种福利
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.02,0:09:14.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.96,0:09:19.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 总是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.97,0:09:22.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个家伙的不长记性真让人佩服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.34,0:09:27.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.77,0:09:32.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.67,0:09:35.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我看来并不需要把他关在外面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.98,0:09:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了 足须小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.65,0:09:39.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撞到头了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.79,0:09:41.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.13,0:09:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 虽然老师确实是色狼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.65,0:09:48.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我觉得他不会趁我们睡着时袭击我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.91,0:09:49.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.92,0:09:52.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一直都很珍惜我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.20,0:09:54.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.89,0:10:00.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次他为了让我们开心 就带我们来旅行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.75,0:10:03.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛…说的也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.19,0:10:05.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少这次就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.53,0:10:10.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们很宠爱徒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.31,0:10:12.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是喜欢他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.96,0:10:14.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.53,0:10:18.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.63,0:10:21.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是觉得他很可怜而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.28,0:10:22.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:24.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.79,0:10:29.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,濑奈小姐不也和我们一起来旅行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.57,0:10:31.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是因为他请客
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.66,0:10:34.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是讨厌的人请客是不会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.23,0:10:37.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.94,0:10:42.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那个我也不是讨厌他啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.48,0:10:44.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但感觉他很恶心…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.54,0:10:47.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都最喜欢老师了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.15,0:10:49.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又没说喜欢他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.80,0:10:50.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:52.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.07,0:10:58.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个爱徒 你可以进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.00,0:11:07.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.15,0:11:13.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想得到大家温暖而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.22,0:11:17.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OP
