Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:52.08,OPjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}私は登ろうかな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.19,0:00:54.83,OPjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}決めて！
